<p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ recipient's copy ]">RC</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Library of Virginia, Richmond ]">Vi</span>); endorsed: Letter from Mr. Jefferson inclosing an act of Congress on the Subject of Western territory &amp; also the Estimates &amp; requisitions for the year 1784. Enclosures (missing) as indicated in letter, endorsement, and entry in <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Jefferson's Summary Journal of Letters written and received ]">SJL</abbr>; see above under 1 Mch. and 5 Apr. 1784. Entry in <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Jefferson's Summary Journal of Letters written and received ]">SJL</abbr> reads: Govr. Inclosed report Western territory and requisitionsadjournment of Congr.commercial subjectLuzerneMarb[ois]Morriss billsLondon news to Mar. 25. ut ante [in entry for letter to Randolph 28 Apr.]</p></div>
